cm-install

USAGE:
    ./cm install
        Installs and configures all formulae present in current working directory

    ./cm install [formula ...]
        Installs and configures each formula

    ./cm install --dry-run [formula ...]
        Lists the formula that will be installed in the order in which they
        will be executed

NOTES:
    Installation order:
        - Look for a formula file in the current working directory. If it
          exists, execute it
        - Repeat the above step for each directory in the current working
          directory
